data.description: Nestled in the heart of south Peach County, this property is an outdoor lover's paradise, offering well OVER 5 ACRES of pristine residential agricultural land. As you enter the estate, you'll be greeted by partially fenced pastures, meticulously designed to accommodate your livestock needs. The woven wire fence, thoughtfully installed, not only ensures the comfort of your animals but also provides ample space for maneuvering your tractor around either side with ease. Just minutes from the interstate, this land allows you to embrace the tranquility of rural living while enjoying the convenience of modern amenities Beyond the pastures, awaits a well maintained ranch home, with a rocking chair porch on a solid slab foundation. Inside, you'll discover an upgraded plumbing system featuring state-of-the-art PEX piping and a water filtration system. The living room features vaulted ceilings and refreshing natural lighting. The kitchen island overlooks a formal dining room that backs up to a walk through pantry and mudroom. Both bathrooms offer generous cabinetry and storage space. The side entrance garage not only adds convenience but also expands the functional square footage of the home, providing ample space for storage or can be converted to an attached workshop. In addition to the garage, there is also a detached shed and covered parking pad. Whether you envision a family farm, a sanctuary for your beloved animals, or a hub for outdoor entertainment, this property provides the perfect canvas with limitless landscape potential. The acreage is already a sweet deal but the home is the icing on the cake. Don't miss the opportunity to make this rare find your own. Come see this in person!
